(IMG:[e-hentai-countdown.darknessfall.com] https://e-hentai-countdown.darknessfall.com/EH-Cdwn.png?auctionname=Kedama's%20Auction&month=12&day=17&year=2016&hour=13&minute=00)
if hv 0.85 is coming before the auction ends,all the bids will be cancelled and items will be returned.
如果0.85在拍卖结束前来临则取消所有出价，物品退回买主。

Rules（must read)

*Item auction will be extended if any bid is made in the last 10mins.it works like below:
the auction end in 21:00，
if you make a valid bid at 20:50~20:59, then this item'll be extended to 21:10 and marked with E1;
if you make a valid bid at 21:00~21:10, then it's extended to 21:20 and marked with E2;
if you make a valid bid after 21:10, then it extend another 10min(11 extend to 21,20 extend to 30).
*End time is subject to the time displayed in your reply(eg. if 9:00pm is the deadline your post@9:00pm is valid，but 9:01pm is invalid.).
*Items will be send to winners with cod after auction end asap.
*All bids are in credits and must be post here.The bid should follow a form like this ''item code+your price''. if current bid>=500k，+xx% is ok.
*Any wrong code or wrong bid is invalid and will be ignored.
*Your bid must be multiple of 10k(I'll round up).
*I'll not update regularly so check the latest post before your bid.
*Do not edit your post,correction should be in a new post. I'll ignore any edited post.
*You can cancel the bid until 2days left.Obvious mistake occurred in the last 30 mins may be canceled but you should make a new reply to explain it with in 5 minutes.(Edit your post is a unstable way because I may update the price before your edit.)
*proxy bids service is off.
*there are too many bids in the last 30min and the price of the 1st page can't be updated immediately.
i suggest you pay attention to the bids made by others on what you want.
*Start bid: 50k except defined ones.
minimum Bid increments:
50k if current bid <500k.
10% if current bid >=500k.I'll round up if your bid is slightly lower than minimum valid bid(like 10k or 20k).Please contact me if someone give an invalid bid but I still update it.If it happened after the auction end,I will send one more cod for the price difference between the invalid bid and the minimum valid bid.
*The winner must clear CoD within 72 hours(if you need more time please contact me before bidding).

Proxy Auction Rules:

*I'd take 10% of the final payment as a charge (free charge if your income <=500k).
*The auction normally start on Wednesday and end on Saturday every week.
*MM me your equipments/items with "Subject name:auction",please name the equip link and it will make my work much easier.
*The auction start price is 50k so if I see your item not worth at least 50k I'll return it.
*You could mention me a higher start price in MM if your item is expensive.


规则说明（出价必读）:

*单件物品拍卖最后10分钟的有效出价会进入加时：
以21:00拍卖结束为例，
20:50~20:59间的有效出价将统一延时至21:10结束，标记为E1；
21:00~21:10间的有效出价将统一延时至21:20结束，标记为E2；
21:10之后的加时为顺延10分钟(21:11顺延至21:21,21:20顺延至21:30）。
*出价时间以系统显示为准(如21:00结束，则21:00出价为有效，21:01出价为无效)。
*拍卖结束后如无特殊情况我会第一时间发cod。
*出价必须在本帖回复包含“物品代码”及价格。标价大于50万后可以用百分比表示加价。
*出价代码错误或价格错误无效。
*出价必需为10k的整数倍（如果没到10%最低出价但我疏忽仍然使用这个出价，拍卖结束后我会另外收取差价）。
*本层价格可能不能经常更新，出价前请留意最新出价贴。
*编辑帖子出价无效，有任何改动请在此贴内发新回复。
*拍卖结束前2天内出价不可撤销。最后三十分钟内的明显的错误出价可能可以被撤销（例如拍错拍品），但是你必
须在五分钟内发新回复来说明，编辑你的帖子来改正可能会因为我在你的编辑之前更新了价格而导致无效。
*代理出价业务不可用。
最后半小时由于出价密集,届时首页标价来不及即时更新。请自行在回复中关注你中意物品的当前出价。
*起拍价5万，物主可自定起拍价。
加价下限说明：
若目前出价低于50万，则每次加价至少5万。
若目前出价≥50万，则每次加价至少10%。如果出价略低于最低可行出价我会向上取整（20k以内）。
*货款必需于cod发出后72小时内付清，如果希望延期付款请于出价前联系我。

拍品接收规则:

*代拍费用为你本期最终收入的10%（如小于等于500k将不收取）。
*拍卖一般在每周三开始，每周六结束。
*请将装备/材料直接mm给我，Subject一栏填“auction”，请附上正确装备链接。
*起拍价格为50k，如果装备很难起拍会被退信。
*你可以设定更高起拍价格，请于信中附上起拍价格。


Feeling the material bidding somewhat boring?

Now I present to you,the Vickrey Auction~


A Vickrey Auction is a type of sealed-bid auction.In brief,the bidder should send the mm with the bid to the auctioner instead of post it.The highest bidder win and pay the second highest price.

For more details,see here:[en.wikipedia.org] https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vickrey_auction

From this week auction,there is always a Vickrey Auction zone.You can bid things by mm me.If you like your materials to sell in a Vickrey way,just send me and notice 'vickrey'in the mail(not in the title)(If you write nothing,it will still sell in the tradition way as default.).
Equipment is welcomed too,but not recommanded.

The bid rules of the Vickrey Auction Area is as follow:

1.One must give the bid to me by moogle mail(only the number,not credit).Write 'Vickrey [item code]'in title.You can recall your mail anytime before the auction end.Post the bid in the forum,incorect title,multiple mails for the same goods,mail after the auction will be ignored.

2.The auctioner must keep all the 'Vickrey [XXX]' title mails unread before the auction end.If any mail is opened before the auction end,or anyone find the mail opened and post it in the forum,then all bid of the item is invalid.(So sorry if I do.I will try avoid doing this.)

3.Give a too 'regular'bid is not recommanded,such as 10k,1m...You can bid the number like 128923,538057,etc.If there is two bidder give the same number,the earlier one who sent the mail win.

4.If there is only one bid to the goods,the only bidder win.

5.If the final price is lower than half of the market price,the bid invalid.

6.I will write the highest and the second,third highest bid and the time they sent the mail,15 minutes after the auction end.

If you have any suggestion,please help me improve it.Thank you and happy bidding~

维克里拍卖上线~
出价者将价格以mm寄给我（只是数字，并非现金），标题格式为：Vickrey [拍品代码]。在拍卖结束后15分钟统一打开信
揭晓前三个最高出价和各自的出价时间，出价最高者赢得拍品但只要付第二高的价格，也就是最高未中标者的价格

具体介绍请看https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vickrey_auction
如果希望以维克里拍卖方式拍卖材料请在信中注明维克里，未注明则默认为普通拍卖，装备也可以，但不建议。
1.单一拍品只能发一次信件，在拍卖结束前可收回，如果多发则视为全部无效。
2. 在拍卖结束前拍主必须保持信件未阅读状态，如果有误打开或者出价者发现信件被打开并在拍卖贴公开，则该项拍
品视为无效。（标题格式错误除外，视为出价无效）
3. 不建议出价数额为规律数字，如100k，1m，以防出价相同情况。如果出现两者出价相同则取发信时间较早的人赢得拍
品。
4.若一项拍品只有一个出价则取唯一的出价者赢得拍品。
5.任何情况下若最终价格小于市价的二分之一则视为出价无效，以保护卖主收益。
